data.description: Beautiful corner lot home! With all the upgrades . You are greeted with the large open concept. Gorgeous kitchen with Quartz countertops,42" inch cabinets, double oven .Surround sound through out, Upgraded lighting and fans throughout the home, smart home features, Living room with extra large sliding glass doors to appreciate the beautiful backyard and light up your living space. 8 ft doors throughout the interior of the home, beautiful flooring, Huge loft area, Large walk in closet in Primary bedroom, Both bathroom have been upgraded to have double sinks, pavers in driveway Epoxy floor in Garage in addition door was an upgraded to have taller doors. Upgraded outlets for outside, Has BBQ hookup out back  pre plumbed for water softener , built in trampoline out back. corner lot, Synthetic grass out back. Low maintenance!  Have to see to appreciate! You will NOT be disappointed.
